FBIS4-12165 "drnes066_s_94007" FBIS-NES-94-066 Daily Report 1 Apr 1994 Iran European Islamic Student Group Praises Khamene'i European Islamic Student Group Praises Khamene'i LD0104141894 Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran in English 1130 GMT 1 Apr 94 LD0104141894 Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran English BFN [Text] The Union of Students Islamic Association in Europe, releasing a statement, congratulated, the April 1, the Islamic Republic Day to the leader of the Islamic revolution and the martyr-nurturing nation of Iran. It has been underlined in the statement that the Muslim people and the world oppressed, adopting the Islamic revolution as a model, are moving in line with destruction of protectors of international plunderers' interests. The statement says: The Iranian Muslim people, displaying Islam's superior power in the face of satanic powers, revived the rays of hope and freedom in the hearts of the Muslim and oppressed peoples adding to the level of their knowledge and vigilance. The Union of Students Islamic Association in Europe, in the statement, called on the world Muslims to adopt Ayatollah Khamene'i's guidelines to pursue the sublime objectives of Islam.
